    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tools used in weaving to beat the weft fiber tightly against previous rows of weaving. Also used in basketry work. Beaters may be of  various shapes, sizes, and materials; may be handheld or incorporated into the mechanism of a loom. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
